<lb n="0030b07" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0030001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】保延三年寫高山寺藏本，【乙】高山寺藏古寫本</note>藥師如來念誦儀軌一卷</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0030b08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030b09" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智
<lb n="0030b10" ed="T"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0030b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0030b1101">佛一時在維那離<note n="0030002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">音樂＝樂音【甲】</note><note n="0030002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">音樂【大】，樂音【甲】</note><app n="0030002"><lem wit="【大】">音樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">樂音</rdg></app>樹下。與<note n="0030003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（大菩薩）ィ＋三【原】</note><note n="0030003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，大菩薩三【校異-原】</note><app n="0030003"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">大菩薩三</rdg></app>萬六千
<lb n="0030b12" ed="T"/>比<note n="0030004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">丘＋（八萬）ィ【原】</note><note n="0030004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">丘【大】，丘八萬【校異-原】</note><app n="0030004"><lem wit="【大】">丘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">丘八萬</rdg></app>人俱。及十二神王。并諸眷屬天龍八部
<lb n="0030b13" ed="T"/>大神王。在如是等大眾會中。說是法已。大眾
<lb n="0030b14" ed="T"/>皆聞無不歡喜。是<note n="0030005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即名＝名即【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0030005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即名【大】，名即【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030005"><lem wit="【大】">即名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">名即</rdg></app>為結願神呪。即薄伽
<lb n="0030b15" ed="T"/>梵說呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0030b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0030b1601" cb:type="dharani">南謨薄伽筏帝鞞殺<note n="0030006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">社＝耶【乙】</note><note n="0030006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">社【大】，耶【乙】</note><app n="0030006"><lem wit="【大】">社</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">耶</rdg></app>寠嚕蔽瑠璃鉢唎婆
<lb n="0030b17" ed="T"/><note n="0030007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">喝＝羯【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0030007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喝【大】，羯【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030007"><lem wit="【大】">喝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羯</rdg></app>囉闍耶怛他揭<note n="0030008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">多＋（耶阿羅歇帝三藐三勃陀耶）【乙】</note><note n="0030008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多【大】，多耶阿羅歇帝三藐三勃陀耶【乙】</note><app n="0030008"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">多耶阿羅歇帝三藐三勃陀耶</rdg></app>怛姪他唵鞞殺<note n="0030009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">逝＋（鞞殺逝）【乙】</note><note n="0030009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">逝【大】，逝鞞殺逝【乙】</note><app n="0030009"><lem wit="【大】">逝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">逝鞞殺逝</rdg></app>鞞
<lb n="0030b18" ed="T"/>殺社<note n="0030010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三沒＝沒哩【乙】</note><note n="0030010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三沒【大】，沒哩【乙】</note><app n="0030010"><lem wit="【大】">三沒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">沒哩</rdg></app>揭帝<note n="0030011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆＝沙【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0030011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆【大】，沙【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030011"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">沙</rdg></app>婆呵</p>
<lb n="0030b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0030b1901">若有受持此真言。能拔身中過去生死一切
<lb n="0030b20" ed="T"/>重罪。不復經歷三<note n="0030012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">塗＝途【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0030012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">塗【大】，途【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030012"><lem wit="【大】">塗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">途</rdg></app>。免離九橫超越眾<note n="0030013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">苦＋（七佛經并陀羅尼集經有此三字）【乙】</note><note n="0030013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">苦【大】，苦七佛經并陀羅尼集經有此三字【乙】</note><app n="0030013"><lem wit="【大】">苦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">苦七佛經并陀羅尼集經有此三字</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0030b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0030b2101">根本印真言。以左右<note n="0030014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔手〕－【乙】</note><note n="0030014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">手【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0030014"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>頭指以下八指。反
<lb n="0030b22" ed="T"/><note n="0030015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔叉〕－【甲】</note><note n="0030015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">叉【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0030015"><lem wit="【大】">叉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>入於掌。以二大指來去呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0030b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0030b2301" cb:type="dharani">唵戰馱祇<note n="0030016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">哩＋（二合）夾註【乙】</note><note n="0030016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哩【大】，哩(二合)【乙】</note><app n="0030016"><lem wit="【大】">哩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">哩<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app><note n="0030017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑＝沙【甲】</note><note n="0030017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娑【大】，沙【甲】</note><app n="0030017"><lem wit="【大】">娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沙</rdg></app>婆呵</p>
<lb n="0030b24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0030b2401"><note n="0030018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔次〕－【甲】</note><note n="0030018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0030018"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>結<note n="0030019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔護〕－【乙】</note><note n="0030019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">護【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0030019"><lem wit="【大】">護</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>讚。</p>
<lb n="0030b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0030b2501" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0030020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（曩莫）＋薩【甲】</note><note n="0030020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">薩【大】，曩莫薩【甲】</note><app n="0030020"><lem wit="【大】">薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">曩莫薩</rdg></app>縛勃馱曩薩縛爾<note n="0030021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">曩＝奈【乙】</note><note n="0030021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曩【大】，奈【乙】</note><app n="0030021"><lem wit="【大】">曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">奈</rdg></app><note place="inline">入</note>迦盧拏怛麼<note place="inline">二合平</note>
<lb n="0030b26" ed="T"/>迦訶羅<note n="0030022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【甲】</note><note n="0030022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0030022"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>覩迷<note place="inline"><note n="0030023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">存＝在【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0030023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">存【大】，在【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030023"><lem wit="【大】">存</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">在</rdg></app>念於我</note>俱嚕吠女哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>入縛
<lb n="0030b27" ed="T"/>羅<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0030024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（入縛羅）＋怛【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0030024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怛【大】，入縛羅怛【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030024"><lem wit="【大】">怛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">入縛羅怛</rdg></app>他誐<note n="0030025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">多麼訶捺＝哆訶摩捨【乙】</note><note n="0030025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多麼訶捺【大】，哆訶摩捨【乙】</note><app n="0030025"><lem wit="【大】">多麼訶捺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">哆訶摩捨</rdg></app>耶<note place="inline"><note n="0030026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（辯才）＋成【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0030026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成【大】，辯才成【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030026"><lem wit="【大】">成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">辯才成</rdg></app>就義</note>曩謨悉羯羅
<lb n="0030b28" ed="T"/><note place="inline">歸命頂禮義</note></p>
<lb n="0030b29" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>藥師<note n="0030027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔如來念誦〕－【甲】</note><note n="0030027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如來念誦【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0030027"><lem wit="【大】">如來<note n="0030028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔念誦〕－【乙】</note><note n="0030028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念誦【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0030028"><lem wit="【大】">念誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>儀軌<note n="0030029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【甲】</note><note n="0030029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0030029"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0030030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲本奧書曰保延三年五月十八日已時許執筆，同時一校了，後世菩提出離生死因也，同年七月二日酉時點了</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>